## 13. High Score Architecture

The leaderboard should support more than one kind of excellence.

### Global Boards

```text
Highest Single Repair
Longest Golden-Seam Combo
Best ZPC Compression
Most Useful Reconstruction
Most Novel Valid Category
Best Cross-Domain Transfer
Most Community-Adopted Repair
Fastest Master Repair
Best Human-AI Team
Best AI Agent
Best New Player
```

### Integrity Rules

- Never reward speed without a quality threshold.
- Similar entries should be clustered before novelty scoring.
- Community voting should be weighted by demonstrated reconstruction ability.
- Popularity must not substitute for coherence.
- A later repair may supersede an earlier one while preserving lineage and credit.
- Contributors to merged repairs retain provenance.

