## 16. Foundational Design Law

Self-reference becomes generative only after foundations become stable.

Hammer Mole therefore teaches in this order:

```text
Feel the word.
Recognize the split.
Name the pieces.
Relate the pieces.
Compress the structure.
Reuse the structure.
Generate descendants.
Reflect on the process itself.
```

The game does not begin with abstraction.

It earns abstraction.

